{"tid":1559573,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[ 緊急幫推 ] 拯救義士！五大訴求立即升級！","createTime":"2019-09-11T01:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T09:25:28.000Z","uid":260988,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"324e3cb3cb9841ba0d86f3102044723edb53a923","tid":1559573,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:17:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">魚蛋革命</span>中黑警嘅暴力，與今次<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港榮光革命</span>並無二致，我哋嘅準則應該一視同仁，齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋爭取到 71 立法會義士如梁繼平等人可以安全回香港，我哋當然都要黃台仰李東昇可以安全返港！<br />\n<br />\n釋放今次<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港榮光革命</span>所有嘅被補示威者，與及釋放<span style=\"color: orange;\">魚蛋革命</span>所有嘅被補示威者！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">釋放梁天琦！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求、缺一不可！</span><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三、撤銷魚蛋革命及香港榮光革命所有抗爭者控罪及判刑</span><br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpVdiY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpVdiY.png&h=45c9f4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gyt3ncF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyt3ncF.jpg&h=9f5d4adb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eae18261e17db115e89825dd2ec8745d332ad19d","tid":1559573,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a418218611fb0c14ed4ea1ea6b882c35494533ed","tid":1559573,"uid":260988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae18261e17db115e89825dd2ec8745d332ad19d","tid":1559573,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T01:22:27.000Z","msg":"謝謝幫推，求正評"},{"pid":"58047fbb3c785b67a8e07dc326a0b0959c66269e","tid":1559573,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime